"True\n"
">>> Color.RED.value in Color\n"
"True"
msgstr ""
">>> some_var = Color.RED\n"
">>> some_var in Color\n"
"True\n"
">>> Color.RED.value in Color\n"
"True"

#: ../../library/enum.rst:221
msgid ""
"Before Python 3.12, a ``TypeError`` is raised if a non-Enum-member is used "
